Package: ggsaver
Title: Easy Saving of ggplot2 Plots
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Eric", "Holt", , "eric.r.pkg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-8945-2947"))
Description: Provides a function to easily save ggplot2 plots to a specified directory. The function can be used to save a series of related plots with minimal code. If no file extension is provided, the plot is saved as a PNG.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: ggplot2
Encoding: UTF-8
